stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Proposed: Parent Agent raises DelegateIntent
  Proposed --> Validated: Structure and scope pass
  Validated --> Rejected: Out of bounds/lack of ability
  Validated --> Running: Permissions allowed
  Running --> NeedsApproval: Sub-Agent requests high-risk actions
  NeedsApproval --> Running: Parent Agent/User Approval
  NeedsApproval --> Constrained: reject and narrow
  Constrained --> Running: Continue to only do the safe subset
  Running --> Completed: Return structured results
  Running --> Failed: Timeout/cancellation/tool ​​failure
  Failed --> Recovered: Parent Agent recycling or reassignment
  Completed --> Joined: Parent Agent review & join
  Recovered --> Joined
  Rejected --> Joined
  Joined --> [*]
